author: Eduonix
message:
Dear Students,
  Hope you're well!  We're excited to announce our new query system to streamline communication. Please take note:  1. **Effective Date**: Starting today, 12th June 2024, submit all non-academic inquiries through our query forum.  2. **Non-Academic Inquiries**: Only queries submitted via the query forum will be accepted. No more calls, WhatsApp, or emails for these.  3. **Academic Inquiries**: Use Microsoft Teams for academic queries and raise a ticket after posting your doubts. No other queries on Teams will be responded to.  4. **Video Guide**: Watch this video to learn how to use the new system: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XgKvh5GeNtneBoYYZeK3JQ8t5udczhuC/view?usp=sharing  5. **Enforcement**: Queries via WhatsApp, phone calls, or outside Teams for academic issues will not be considered.  6. **Reminder Desk**: Our Support Contact is now our Reminder Desk, sending only session reminders. No other queries will be addressed here.  Thanks for your cooperation!  Best, Team Eduonix
